<!doctype html>
<%-include header%>
<style type="text/css">
	.login-advise-title{
		height:30px;
		line-height: 30px;
		font-size: 14px;
		margin-top: 10px;
		border-radius: 5px;
		background-color: #FFFFFF;
		padding-left: 10px;
		opacity: .8;
		background-color: rgb(189, 54, 47);
		background-image: linear-gradient(rgb(238, 95, 91), rgb(189, 54, 47));
		background-position: 0px -15px;
		background-repeat: repeat-x;
		border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
		border-bottom-left-radius: 6px;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 6px;
		border-bottom-style: solid;
		border-bottom-width: 1px;
		border-image-outset: 0 0 0 0;
		border-image-repeat: stretch stretch;
		border-image-slice: 100% 100% 100% 100%;
		border-image-source: none;
		border-image-width: 1 1 1 1;
		border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-left-style: solid;
		border-left-width: 1px;
		border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-right-style: solid;
		border-right-width: 1px;
		border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-top-left-radius: 6px;
		border-top-right-radius: 6px;
		border-top-style: solid;
		border-top-width: 1px;
		box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) 0px 1px 0px 0px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 1px 2px 0px;
		color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
		cursor: pointer;
		font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
		margin-bottom: 0px;
		outline-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
		outline-style: none;
		outline-width: 0px;
		text-align: left;
		text-decoration: none;
		text-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25) 0px -1px 0px;
		transition-delay: 0s;
		transition-duration: 0.1s;
		transition-property: background-position;
		transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0, 0, 1, 1);
		vertical-align: middle;
		-moz-border-bottom-colors: none;
		-moz-border-left-colors: none;
		-moz-border-right-colors: none;
		-moz-border-top-colors: none;
		-moz-text-blink: none;
		-moz-text-decoration-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);
		-moz-text-decoration-line: none;
		-moz-text-decoration-style: solid;
	}
	.login-advise-title:hover{
		opacity: 1.0;
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	.login-advise-content{
		margin-top: 2px;
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		display: inline-block;
	}
	.login-advise-content .arrow{
		margin-left: 40px;
		border-right-color: transparent;
		border-right-style: solid;
		border-right-width: 11px;
		border-top-color: transparent;
		border-top-style: solid;
		border-top-width: 0px;
		border-bottom-color: #FFFFFF;
		border-bottom-style: solid;
		border-bottom-width: 11px;
		border-left-color: transparent;
		border-left-style: solid;
		border-left-width: 11px;
		display: block;
		font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		height: 0px;
		left: -11px;
		line-height: 20px;
		position: absolute;
		text-align: left;
		top: 0px;
		white-space: normal;
		width: 0px;
	}
	.login-advise-content .text{
		margin-top: 10px;
		display: block;
		border-radius: 5px;
		padding:10px;
		word-break:break-all;
		text-indent: 2em;

		background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);
		background-image: linear-gradient(rgb(255, 255, 255), rgb(230, 230, 230));
		background-position: 0% 0%;
		background-repeat: repeat-x;
		border-bottom-color: rgb(179, 179, 179);
		border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
		border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
		border-bottom-style: solid;
		border-bottom-width: 1px;
		border-image-outset: 0 0 0 0;
		border-image-repeat: stretch stretch;
		border-image-slice: 100% 100% 100% 100%;
		border-image-source: none;
		border-image-width: 1 1 1 1;
		border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-left-style: solid;
		border-left-width: 1px;
		border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-right-style: solid;
		border-right-width: 1px;
		border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		border-top-left-radius: 4px;
		border-top-right-radius: 4px;
		border-top-style: solid;
		border-top-width: 1px;
		box-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2) 0px 1px 0px 0px inset, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 1px 2px 0px;
		color: rgb(51, 51, 51);
		cursor: pointer;
		font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;
		font-size: 14px;
		line-height: 20px;
		list-style-image: none;
		list-style-position: outside;
		list-style-type: none;
		margin-bottom: 0px;
		outline-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);
		outline-style: none;
		outline-width: 0px;
		text-decoration: none;
		text-shadow: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75) 0px 1px 1px;
		transition-delay: 0s;
		transition-duration: 0s;
		transition-property: all;
		transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1);
		vertical-align: middle;
		-moz-border-bottom-colors: none;
		-moz-border-left-colors: none;
		-moz-border-right-colors: none;
		-moz-border-top-colors: none;
		-moz-text-blink: none;
		-moz-text-decoration-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);
		-moz-text-decoration-line: none;
		-moz-text-decoration-style: solid;

	}
	.login-advise-content .text a{
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style>
<div class='container'>
	<div style='margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:200px;'>
		<h3 style='padding-left:10px;'>
			登录帮助
		</h3>
		<div id="" class="login-advise-title">
			密码丢失
		</div><!-- / -->
		<div class='login-advise-content'>
			<div class='arrow'></div>
			<div class='text'>
				如果您的密码丢失或者遗忘，您可以通过<a href='/losePwd'>密码找回</a>来修改您的密码，您不需要已经遗失的密码来认证您的身份，我们会通过您申请账户时使用的邮箱使您重新设置密码！
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="" class="login-advise-title">
			忘记账户
		</div><!-- / -->
		<div class='login-advise-content'>
			<div class='arrow'></div>
			<div class='text'>
				如果您申请过我们的账户并且但是忘记了的名称导致您无法登录，我们建议您通过邮箱进行账户找回，或者直接通过邮箱进行登录，我们已经完善了<a href='/login'>邮箱登录</a>的技术，因此，在您通过邮箱登录后可以通过账户设置重新修改您的账户名称，不过，千万不要忘记了您申请时候所使用的邮箱哦，如果您忘记了申请时候所使用的邮箱，那么管理员也无法帮您找回啦，要是这样，我们建议您<a href='/reg'>重新申请</a>一个账户，不会浪费时间的哦！
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="" class="login-advise-title">
			输入失效
		</div><!-- / -->
		<div class='login-advise-content'>
			<div class='arrow'></div>
			<div class='text'>
				如果您输入账户密码时提醒您输入失效，可能是由于以下几个方面引起的：<br />
				1.输入的用户名不正确：数字、字母、下划线<br />
				2.用户名、密码不允许为空：不允许输入空格，空格不是有效的字符<br />
				3.确定您是否启用了键盘大写功能：用户名和密码会区分大小写
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="" class="login-advise-title">
			浏览器兼容
		</div><!-- / -->
		<div class='login-advise-content'>
			<div class='arrow'></div>
			<div class='text'>
				建议您使用火狐、chrome、opera、safari等支持html5以及css3的浏览器，若您使用的是IE，请最少升级到IE9,谢谢！<br />
				我们会努力的做到浏览器兼容，以保证您的使用习惯！
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="" class="login-advise-title">
			错误报告
		</div><!-- / -->
		<div class='login-advise-content'>
			<div class='arrow'></div>
			<div class='text'>
				如果您不能正常访问登录页或者登录后出现错误内容，这可能是由于服务器引起的，通常错误代码包括404,500等，404指的是无法找到的登录页面或者登录后指向错误的跳转页，500指的是服务器错误，通常这样的错误是由于网站的后台代码引起的，如果遇到此错误，您可以等待一段时间，管理员会进行修复，或者您可以联系我们，请发邮件至<font color='blue'>huanhai24@sina.com</font>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<%-include comment_user_control%>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
	$(document).ready(function(){
		(function(){
			$.fn.collapseTips = function(options){
				var defaults = {
					collapse : true
				};
				var $otps = $.extend({} , defaults , options);
				if($opts.collapse === true)
				{
					$(this).each(function(){
						var f = 1 ; 
						$(this).click(function(){
							if(f === 0)
							{
								$(this).next('.login-advise-content').css({
									'display':'inline-block'
								});
								f = 1;
							}
							else if(f === 1)
							{
								$(this).next('.login-advise-content').css({
									'display':'none'
								});
								f = 0;
							}
						});
					});
				}
			};
		})(jQuery);
	});
	$('.login-advise-title').collapseTips({
		collapse : false
	});
</script>